reviewText: I find it quite irregular that the 2nd story, featuring Chad King as the father, has no mention of Chad.

Dear Amazon,

I would love nothing more than to review this movie. It has now been 21 since i ordered this movie.

I saw this film at the 2009 Philadelphia Film Festival and it blew me away. Brilliant acting and gripping stories. I can see why it won Best Picture.

It may not be for everyone, but it definitely left an impact on me.
